* '''Hetty:''' So what have you found so far?
* '''Player:''' I'm afraid I don't have any of them yet.
* '''Hetty:''' Well I can't make the potion without them! Remember... You need an eye of newt, a rat's tail, an onion, and a piece of burnt meat. Off you go dear!
* {{tact|end}}

